data.title: Episode 2739 (1 June 2004)
data.meta_description: The big day dawns and Nana begins to get the jitters, worrying that she is betraying her first husband by remarrying. Alfie is also worried, but for a different reason - Wilfred is nowhere to be found. As Nana waits at the altar, Alfie goes on a frantic search for the groom. The Ferreiras...
data.text:
Nana excitedly gets ready for the wedding. Wilfred joylessly does. Nana smiles at the brooch William gave her - she worries she's betrayed him. Kat says that you forgive the person you love, no matter what they do.

Yolande tells Alfie that Wilfred's left. He catches up with him at the tube station - he says he's ill. Alfie discovers he has stolen his granddad's medals.

Tariq barricades the door. Ronny and Kareena ring up about flats. The bailiffs arrive. Ronny is angry. Adi arrives with a mortgage offer, but they still get evicted.

Chrissie babysits the Beale kids.

Kat tells Dennis to stop leering at Zoe.

Mickey makes a mess with the confetti.

Sonia and Martin get fed up with Pauline and Dot interfering.

Den upsets Chrissie.
